description:
Cycle Around Japan: A Journey Across Hokkaido

Travel Documentary hosted by Chris Wells, published by NHK in 2015 - English narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/0/03/Cycle-Around-Japan-A-Journey-Across-Hokkaido-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
Zac Reynols visits Hokkaido. His two-wheeled adventures include a ride through the stunning lavender fields of Furano, experiencing the unique Ainu culture, and tasting some of the wonderful local food. Zac also offers practical tips on bike touring.
